com.mastergaurav.android.common.xml

类 ClassInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mastergaurav.android.common.xml.ClassInfo

  • public class ClassInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a map between a model class and element name in XML.
    This class is used by XMLDeserializer to identify the mapping between an element (via its name) and the type that it maps to.
    See XMLDeserializer for more details on its usage
    另请参阅:
    XMLDeserializer
